#    Setup: https://cloud.mongodb.com (get connection string)
#    When: Working with document databases
#
# 3. ATLASSIAN (Jira+Confluence) - Issue tracking and documentation
#    Setup: https://id.atlassian.com/manage-profile/security/api-tokens
#    When: Managing issues, publishing docs
